me":"2020-09-14T05:27:06.000Z","msg":"【無條件義助】內地執法機關再次成功為香港緝拿重犯<br />\n<br />\n本月六日，香港元朗發生謀殺案，一名17歲青年死亡，而27歲男疑兇則潛逃回內地。警方其後向公安部、廣東省公安廳及深圳市公安局要求協助，疑凶最後在內地落網。<br />\n<br />\n香港警方感謝公安部、廣東省公安廳及深圳市公安局的全力協助，該名疑犯最終在內地落網，不但標誌着兩地警方對聯合打擊罪行的決心，更清晰地表達兩地警方對維護社會法治的信念。元朗警區重案組現正積極調查案件。<br />\n<br />\n失憶藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b59a533b1248143aad5c7cebc28fa87710aa7e","tid":2201751,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:27:25.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90569331c4e632f3bc516b605c6b0fca5cbca05c","tid":2201751,"uid":96871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:28:15.000Z","msg":"呢d真係死仆街黎"},{"pid":"d3dc738d41d7cd8991e38a1249156c4125c8d1a5","tid":2201751,"uid":265338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:29:50.000Z","msg":"成功你都冇權架啦，地方立例管中央呀？"},{"pid":"56fbea4fb69671bd49a86bea4e303a896b079641","tid":2201751,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca40fc4cf4ce70e7e75d363daeec59a0346a2a04","tid":2201751,"uid":20563,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:01:58.000Z","msg":"湯渣驊詭辯<br />\n<br />\n立法會文件講到明有行政手段移交疑犯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yh7EftJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYh7EftJ.png&h=fbcbd3c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n份野就唔係近期寫既，係2001年出<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQ6EZVo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQ6EZVo.png&h=71e1ba22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2001年湯渣驊做緊乜？咪就係立法會議員囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https:/